data.description: Welcome Home!  Gorgeous, cozy home available in the Wooden Eagle Subdivision in Kathleen!  This meticulously maintained 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home offers a perfect blend of modern elegance and comfort.  Immerse yourself in spacious rooms, a beautiful kitchen/dining area, large pantry space, newly renovated primary bathroom, large walk-in closet, and roomy back deck overlooking a serene, private backyard retreat.  HVAC only 2 years old!  Located near a cul-de-sac in a well sought-after neighborhood, this residence provides both tranquility and convenience.  Don't miss the opportunity to call this stunning property your new home sweet home!
